{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, he was in front of me, and I was the second row back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he jumped, and I went for the ball.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I hit him in the back of the head with the palm of my hand and knocked his feet totally out from under him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then I didn't remember that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had to go-- he was unconscious from that, plus he went-- I knocked him unconscious when I hit him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was an accident.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I didn't-- but when he hit the ground, he was unconscious, and he hit the-- his head hit the ground again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so the medics came, and they gave him some sniffers and checked him all over and took him away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "He was just-- but he reminded me that, you're the guy that hit me playing volleyball and knocked me unconscious.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I-- and I said-- now, I remember that happening after he told me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I-- but I had forgotten about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, and that was my point.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some of these guys-- this little guy's wife used to come out to the camp and see Captain Goldbald and talk about her husband, wanted to make sure he was being taken care of.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That he was getting proper nourishment and, you know, was being discriminated against and all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she was out there two or three times a week, had a car and everything, and then had a nice apartment in Corvallis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And her husband was a-- he was a-- he was trying harder than the normal guy to make it, because he had a disadvantage.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He owned a business someplace in New York.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He didn't have to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was soft hands.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
